    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Given these descrete probabilties and outcomes, we can calculate the expected utility  of  $u(x) = - \\mathrm{e}(-\\rho x)$ by multiplying probabilites by outcomes in terms of utility: "
