        "\n",
        "Let us now try to compare this with our apporxmated expeted utility above. If we have a standard normal distribution, so $\\sigma=1$ and $\\mu=0$. The risk aversion coefficient is  $\\rho=5$. The exact and approximate expected utility is"
      ],
